# WordPress Full-Stack Test Task

## Project Overview

This project is a WordPress environment configured via Docker Compose. It includes:

* A custom WordPress theme based on a provided Marvel Figma design.
* A custom WordPress plugin that adds a "Contact us" form with integration to HubSpot and email notifications.
* Proper logging, validation, and error handling.

